{"tid":412551,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"大家按感覺會點排呢6種公共交通公具嘅安全度?","createTime":"2017-09-24T18:03:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T11:27:52.000Z","uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"962b8af01d1d9351bff8cb5a64300b18c38b9d18","tid":412551,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T18:03:10.000Z","msg":"近排深水埗發生左單好嚴重嘅交通意外 RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時深夜都幾常搭巴士 而家搭都有啲驚<br />\n就諗下 大家按感覺會點排呢6種公共交通公具嘅安全度?<br />\n(由最安全到最唔安全)<br />\n<br />\n我會咁排:<br />\n1)鐵路<br />\n2)電車<br />\n3)的士<br />\n4)巴士<br />\n5)小巴<br />\n6)飛機<br />\n<br />\n鐵路唔會抄車 只係驚有啲痴線佬放火放毒器無得走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n電車行得幾慢下 感覺上比較安全 所以第2<br />\n的士 覺得細架啲 有咩危險容易啲避 第3<br />\n巴士始終大架啲 有咩危險好大件事 我自己就多數揀錯下層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小巴成日都渣到識飛咁 所以尾2<br />\n最尾飛機 我知發生意外係好少可<br />\n但感覺始終有啲唔好<br />\n有無人同我一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc4ec05a8e9a8afeeec2afc7a56277425d03e5e","tid":412551,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T18:04:26.000Z","msg":"鐵路唔會抄車 只係驚有啲痴線佬放火放毒<span style=\"color: red;\">氣</span>無得走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1b510077e0bdb2d1f71613db9e43d67f9c54e45","tid":412551,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T18:04:33.000Z","msg":"小巴=的士&gt;All"},{"pid":"4859129dce1369280691fc55c1c82fce67d41488","tid":412551,"uid":80107,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T18:04:42.000Z","msg":"小巴一定擺咗最尾先"},{"pid":"80014e7ba1910f35b67e8dcba2f9f0e4ecb4e1d5","tid":412551,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T18:04:47.000Z","msg":"鐵路點解唔