{"pid":"8ba22478c38a4b13015eb4102972b49f1af104d7","tid":412551,"uid":12557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T20:52:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>話小巴安全果啲一定係唔記得呢單野<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20151219/19418487\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20151219%2F19418487&d=oymE8WJClX8JhFwnOdnowP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=ae214edd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20151219%2F19418487&h=c6240400\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20151219/19418487</a><br />\n<br />\n個人覺得大型車安全過細車<br />\n車撞車本身架車都硬過人<br />\n速度又唔快 撞都冇咁傷咁</blockquote><br />\n照計<br />\ncollision Force=m(delta_v)/(delta_t)<br />\n大嘅車行慢啲<br />\n細嘅車行快啲<br />\n好難比較<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係要計入面d 人受力，唔係俾車撞個力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁要睇個人點坐同埋幾重好多因素喎<br />\n架車撞得大力啲入面啲人先有機會受到多啲力<br />\n啱唔啱先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔岩<br />\n你唔使理架車撞幾大力<br />\n剩係計人嘅減速度就得<br />\n架車撞擊力有10tons 都好，如果冇咩減速，入面嘅人都唔會到咩力<br />\n因為大車質量大，速度又多數比較低<br />\n減速會比較細車小<br />\n所以乘客受力都會小"},{"pid":"2ed65a24963c4e18cd8f58a2b7b78f8d9771d04f","tid":412551,"uid":100499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T20:58:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飛機&gt;鐵路&gt;電車&gt;巴士&gt;的士&gt;渡輪&gt;小巴</blockquote><br />\n渡輪咁後？"},{"pid":"c9b4c14f46aaa6afe395cdf68a0c9c98c72db1f6","tid":412551,"uid":49153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T21:08:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>飛機&gt;鐵路&gt;電車&gt;巴士&gt;的士&gt;渡輪&gt;小巴</blockquote><br />\n渡輪咁後？</blockquote><br />\n搖到咁 <br />\n一個企唔穩就仆